item.title: Monday August 27, 2007 Santa Barbara Tech Talk featuring Gary Woods and Baron Ron Herron
item.description:
Here's the broadcast from Monday, August 27, 2007. Today we looked at an attachment for your iPod called iKaraoke. It comes with a microphone and suppresses the vocal which is good because you didn't did that losers help anyway. Out to the right is a picture of the iKaraoke.
